    decentralized community. The content and opinions expressed on this website
    do not necessarily reflect those of Hooman Digital. This website provides
    links to information, projects, dApps, cryptocurrency exchanges, and various
    other services for public access. Hooman Digital does not guarantee the
    accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the information provided by these
    external websites. We are not responsible for the content of these websites
    and expressly disclaim any liability for damages of any kind resulting from
    the use, reference to, or reliance on any information contained within these
    websites. If you identify an error or issue on this website, please contact
    us at hoomandigital18@gmail.com.
  </p>
</footer>
